                        operator of the asset refered to.
                    </xs:documentation>
                    <xs:documentation cimp:category="TagValue" cimp:subcategory="ESMPRG">1</xs:documentation>
                    <xs:documentation cimp:category="TagValue" cimp:subcategory="ETSOBusinessTerm">
